name: vcui
description: CUI of the versioned SRC concept for a source

name: rcui
description: CUI of the root SRC concept for a source

name: vsab
description: The versioned source abbreviation for a source, e.g., NDDF_2004_11_03

name: rsab
description: The root source abbreviation, for a source e.g. NDDF

name: son
description: The official name for a source

name: sf
description: The Source Family for a source

name: sver
description: The source version, e.g., 2001

name: vstart
description: The date a source became active, e.g., 2001_04_03

name: vend
description: The date a source ceased to be active, e.g., 2001_05_10

name: imeta
description: The version of the Metathesaurus a source first appeared, e.g., 2001AB

name: rmeta
description: The version of the Metathesaurus a source was removed, e.g., 2001AC

name: slc
description: The source license contact information. A semi-colon separated list containing the following fields: Name; Title; Organization; Address 1; Address 2; City; State or Province; Country; Zip or Postal Code; Telephone; Contact Fax; Email; URL

name: scc
description: The source content contact information. A semi-colon separated list containing the following fields: Name; Title; Organization; Address 1; Address 2; City; State or Province; Country; Zip or Postal Code; Telephone; Contact Fax; Email; URL

name: srl
description: 0,1,2,3,4 - explained in the License Agreement.

name: tfr
description: The number of terms for this source in RXNCONSO.RRF, e.g., 12343 (not implemented yet)

name: cfr
description: The number of CUIs associated with this source, e.g., 10234 (not implemented yet)

name: cxty
description: The type of relationship label (Section 2.4.2 of UMLS Reference Manual)

name: ttyl
description: Term type list from source, e.g., MH,EN,PM,TQ

name: atnl
description: The attribute name list, e.g., MUI,RN,TH,...

name: lat
description: The language of the terms in the source

name: cenc
description: Character set as specified by the IANA official names for character assignments http://www.iana.org/assignments/character-sets

name: curver
description: A Y or N flag indicating whether or not this row corresponds to the current version of the named source

name: sabin
description: A Y or N flag indicating whether or not this row is represented in the current MetamorphoSys subset. Initially always Y where CURVER is Y, but later is recomputed by MetamorphoSys.

name: ssn
description: The short name of a source as used by the NLM Knowledge Source Server.

name: scit
description: Citation information for a source. A semi-colon separated list containing the following fields: Author(s); Author(s) address; Author(s) organization; Editor(s); Title; Content Designator; Medium Designator; Edition; Place of Publication; Publisher; Date of Publication/copyright; Date of revision; Location; Extent; Series; Availability Statement (URL); Language; Notes
